mplete set of <span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--yellow\"><strong>PBR textures</strong></span> for all engines.<br><br><span>➤</span><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--green\"><strong> Instructions for use:&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span>Download the .mhpkg from this FAB listing.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Create a folder called \"Outfits\" in your content browser.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Drag your ***.mhpkg into your new \"Outfits\" folder.&nbsp; It should unpack here.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Drag WI_*** asset into the Outfit Clothing section in Metahuman Creator and double click to apply it.</span></p></li></ul>","isAiForbidden":true,"isAiGenerated":false,"lastUpdatedAt":"","listingType":"3d-model","media":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/72b0ea01-4393-4798-a351-ad85a7ac032c/0eeee440-b13c-40c8-a176-f3e00e3b868c.jpg","publishedAt":"2026-02-25T09:07:43.559140Z","reviewCount":0,"thumbnail":"https://media.fab.com/image_previews/gallery_images/4b8dfd81-3321-4e40-a9eb-9ef11b7f915c/175f30ca-23e1-4053-a564-2285eed56b7f.jpg","title":"Casual T Shirt Outfit - Metahuman","uid":"eebd9e12-a4d2-498f-9dee-3943bbe99dab","updatedAt":"","user":{"coverImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-jd7cbln86j8cqf3nl86nv7mx55zzxb/cover/0318ccfa.jpg","profileImageUrl":"https://cdn1.epicgames.com/fab/seller/o-jd7cbln86j8cqf3nl86nv7mx55zzxb/profile/7e6fa5df.jpg","sellerName":"Quantum Assets","uid":"67526019-59bf-4ff3-aab9-b3ee7ed062d0"},"tags":[{"name":"Street","slug":"street","uid":"1714b21a-573d-4d0e-aa60-faa1144f56e0"},{"name":"Shirt","slug":"shirt","uid":"24bc1374-598c-4d05-94db-ed02283470fc"},{"name":"Jeans","slug":"jeans","uid":"5d1f5581-3e97-47eb-8e2e-a75b9afcc227"},{"name":"Cloth","slug":"cloth","uid":"66a612e2-eef0-4dd3-9cee-06aa4b02b4d8"},{"name":"Wardrobe","slug":"wardrobe","uid":"7a7a9c1c-6421-495e-9db6-0d120bb0406e"},{"name":"Casualwear","slug":"casualwear","uid":"8a90b2b6-34dc-4e50-872a-092e804b8d59"},{"name":"Casual","slug":"casual"